{"tid":1653780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強: 警方會埋伏進行拘捕行動","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T20:46:19.000Z","uid":101345,"like":70,"dislike":311,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"14d55e984c83aa4899dff09d40dc4e930f068e1b","tid":1653780,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"琴日hyperkick, 360, 同天水圍事件已經證實狗會埋伏捉人<br />\n不如大家收手回歸和理非啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔好進行反埋伏屠狗</span><br />\n一陣傷到狗失民意呀<br />\n<br />\n&quot;鄧炳強說，自製汽油彈成為常用的暴力手法，有人向警車投擲汽油彈導致警車陷入火海，旺角警署亦曾在短時間內被投擲多枚汽油彈，批評暴徒的行為邪惡，目無法紀，超出市民可接受範圍，強調警方會果斷執法，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>調配資源快速應變及埋伏進行拘捕行動。</strong></span><br />\n&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486097-20191014.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486097-20191014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DArtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=6ca4211c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486097-20191014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c2985f71\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486097-20191014.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5603929feb64605018b5c64e4912ee2dba7a6047","tid":1653780,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17a47d7271e66d0a86e5b5e53fec3ffb9565401b","tid":1653780,"uid":13936,"like":28,"dislike":11,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾ＰＯＳＴ拉　ＢＬＯＣＫＥＤ"},{"pid":"7324d8d55a3d5d303a9f43056efe28aa55425446","tid":1653780,"uid":42548,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"你伏人，人地咪伏番你囉，七頭，公平公正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1338b452855dc906fdf96cde54ef1bc6a11ca7","tid":1653780,"uid":186071,"like":97,"dislike":9,"score":88,"